rl>/RXLImages/1013/hotel1203688-Orologio-Hotel_ext_Thumbnailed.jpg</Url><Width>70</Width><Height>70</Height><Bytes>2644</Bytes><Caption /><ThumbnailUrl>/RXLImages/1013/hotel1203688-Orologio-Hotel_ext_Thumbnailed.jpg</ThumbnailUrl><ThumbnailWidth>70</ThumbnailWidth><ThumbnailHeight>70</ThumbnailHeight><ThumbnailBytes>2632</ThumbnailBytes><PhotoType>ExternalViewOfTheHotel</PhotoType></Photo><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>General</Type><Text>The Art Hotel Orologio is a 3 star property overlooking Piazza Maggiore, one of the most beautiful Italian medieval squares. The hotel is located just in front of the Town Hall and the ancient clock tower, from which it takes its name. The strategic position offers splendid panoramic views over the most important monuments of the city. The surrounding area is fully pedestrianised and major sights like the Towers of Bologna are within easy walking distance. There are also excellent bus links in the vicinity, providing easy access to Bologna Central Station. The hotel is housed in a traditional 7 storey building with terracotta coloured facade. Onsite facilities include a free internet point and free bike rental. There is also free Wi-Fi internet access throughout the premises for ultimate convenience. There is a small bar, plus a buffet breakfast is provided each morning. For evening dining opportunities there are a wealth of fine restaurants in the local area. Standard guestrooms are elegantly decorated with dark wood furniture and marble bathrooms. Amenities include air conditioning, satellite TV, a safe and mini-bar. A private garage is also available onsite.</Text></Description><Amenity><Code>Safe</Code><Text>Safe</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>AirConditioning</Code><Text>Air conditioning</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>RoomService</Code><Text>Room service</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>HairDryer</Code><Text>Hair dryer</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Bar</Code><Text>Bar</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>PublicInternetAcces